《'''記憶編織者'''》（{{lang-en|'''''Stitchers'''''}}）是一部於[[ABC家庭|ABC Family]]／[[Freeform|Freeform]]首播的美國影集。講述利用人死後腦內記憶還能存在48小時，將人的意識連接到死人的腦內記憶，以此偵破每一件懸疑謀殺案。2014年9月29日獲得預訂，<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2014/09/abc-family-picks-up-stitchers-and-young-hungry-cancels-mystery-girls-passes-on-unstrung-843037/|title=ABC Family Picks Up 'Stitchers' And 'Young & Hungry', Cancels 'Mystery Girls', Passes On 'Unstrung'|last=Andreeva|first=Nellie|date=September 29, 2014|work=Deadline.com|accessdate=April 4, 2015|archive-date=2021-02-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210214075254/https://deadline.com/2014/09/abc-family-picks-up-stitchers-and-young-hungry-cancels-mystery-girls-passes-on-unstrung-843037/|dead-url=no}}</ref> 2015年6月2日正式首播。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://variety.com/2015/tv/news/stitchers-abc-family-watch-trailer-video-1201461141/|title=ABC Family Adds 'Covert Affairs' Actor to Summer Crime Procedural 'Stitchers'|date=March 26, 2015|last=Wagmeister|first=Elizabeth|work=[[綜藝_(雜誌)|綜藝雜誌]]|accessdate=April 4, 2015|archive-date=2019-11-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191130210710/https://variety.com/2015/tv/news/stitchers-abc-family-watch-trailer-video-1201461141/|dead-url=no}}</ref> 2015年7月14日，ABC Family宣布續訂第二季。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/2015/07/14/stitchers-renewed-for-season-2-by-abc-family/431097/ |title=‘Stitchers’ Renewed for Season 2 by ABC Family |last=Bibel |first=Sara |date=July 14, 2015 |work=[[TV_by_the_Numbers|TV by the Numbers]] |accessdate=July 15, 2015 |archive-date=2016-06-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160610195625/http://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/2015/07/14/stitchers-renewed-for-season-2-by-abc-family/431097/ |dead-url=yes }}</ref> 2016年10月6日，Freeform宣布續訂第三季。<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://variety.com/2016/tv/news/stitchers-renewed-season-3-freeform-1201880244/|title=‘Stitchers’ Renewed for Season 3 at Freeform|last=Wagmeister|first=Elizabeth|date=2016-10-06|newspaper=綜藝雜誌|language=en-US|access